        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">The concept refers to an absolute temperature, not to be mistaken with temperature difference.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">To express that an object has a temperature, the property &apos;intensive bearer of&apos; can be used. It implies a chain of: object consists of some portion of matter and portion of matter bearer of some temperature.</rdfs:comment>
